title: Ep. - 499 - MIKE AND MARYSE MIZANIN HALFTIME AND LOVE ON THE SPECTRUM
description:
Mike and Maryse Mizanin from Miz & Mrs, which documents their lives as married WWE superstars, discuss their climb to success and this season of their show.

 

Chris Farah reviews Love on Spectrum, a Netflix documentary series following young adults on the autism spectrum as they explore the unpredictable world of love, dating and relationships.

 

Chris and Kate review Halftime, a Netflix documentary which follows Jennifer Lopez from the day of her 50th birthday celebrations to the Super Bowl half-time show she co-headlined with Shakira in 2020.
